# Void Linux Tier 1 Mirrors
#
# Tier 1 mirrors are maintained by the Void Linux Infrastructure Team.
# These mirrors sync directly from the build servers and will always have
# the latest packages available.
#
# Format: URL | Region | Location

https://repo-fastly.voidlinux.org/current | Global | Fastly CDN
https://repo-fi.voidlinux.org/current | Europe | Helsinki, Finland
https://repo-de.voidlinux.org/current | Europe | Frankfurt, Germany
https://mirrors.servercentral.com/voidlinux/current | North America | Chicago, USA
